Package: NUSS
Title: What the Package Does (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Oskar", "Kosch", , "contact@oskarkosch.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2697-1393"))
Description: This package segments short texts - like hashtags -
    into the separated words sequence. It does so with the use of dictionary,
    and may utilize custom words. Since hashtags might be single words,
    unigram approach is employed.
